<emphasis id="A3C3EADAFFB6FFAFD5DF8B28FD0DF895" bold="true" box="[199,679,1842,1869]" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">New record for the Matina River basin</emphasis>
; previous records of the species in 
<collectingRegion id="5373F82AFFB6FFAFD15E8B28FB2CF894" box="[1094,1158,1843,1869]" country="New Zealand" name="West Coast" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">Costa</collectingRegion>
Rican freshwaters were restricted to the Tortuguero and Parismina River basins. 
<emphasis id="A3C3EADAFFB6FFAFD6018B4CFB85F8A8" bold="true" box="[793,1071,1878,1905]" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">New elevational record</emphasis>
(
<specimenCount id="87B1FD41FFB6FFAFD1588B4CFBD2F8AB" box="[1088,1144,1879,1906]" pageId="10" pageNumber="11" type="generic">
<quantity id="564F9B2DFFB6FFAFD1588B4CFBDEF8AB" box="[1088,1140,1879,1906]" metricMagnitude="0" metricUnit="m" metricValue="7.0" pageId="10" pageNumber="11" unit="m" value="7.0">7 m</quantity>
.
</specimenCount>
a.s.l.); previous records of the species in 
<collectingRegion id="5373F82AFFB6FFAFD4218B60FED3F84C" box="[313,377,1915,1941]" country="New Zealand" name="West Coast" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">Costa</collectingRegion>
Rican freshwaters were restricted to 
<quantity id="564F9B2DFFB6FFAFD6388B60FCDAF84C" box="[800,880,1915,1941]" metricMagnitude="0" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.5" metricValueMax="3.0" metricValueMin="0.0" pageId="10" pageNumber="11" unit="m" value="1.5" valueMax="3.0" valueMin="0.0">
0– 
<specimenCount id="87B1FD41FFB6FFAFD6268B60FCDAF84C" box="[830,880,1915,1941]" pageId="10" pageNumber="11" type="generic">3 m</specimenCount>
</quantity>
.a.s.l. 
<emphasis id="A3C3EADAFFB6FFAFD6B48B61FB3DF84C" bold="true" box="[940,1175,1914,1941]" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">Basis of the record:</emphasis>
Three specimens were captured in the río Moín, at the Puerto Fluvial JAPDEVA, 
<collectingRegion id="5373F82AFFB6FFAFD6388B84FCC1F860" box="[800,875,1951,1977]" country="Costa Rica" name="Limon" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">Limón</collectingRegion>
(
<geoCoordinate id="F483500FFFB6FFAFD6618B85FC4DF860" box="[889,999,1950,1977]" degrees="09.99745" direction="north" orientation="latitude" pageId="10" pageNumber="11" precision="1" value="9.99745">09.99745</geoCoordinate>
